      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing dependable daily transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car's exterior and interior show visible signs of use, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some wear on the upholstery. It has been well-maintained mechanically, but it is not a showpiece. If you are looking for a functional, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model, this is a solid choice.",
