    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant rust, major dents, and a peeling clear coat across several panels. Mechanically, the car requires substantial repairs, and the interior has heavy wear, including torn seating and non-functional electronics. It is not currently in reliable driving condition and will need to be towed.",
