      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great parked in the driveway. I've taken good care of it, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the new-car price tag. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
