      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This unit features the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering precise shift throws coupled with a mechanical limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Maintenance is up to date, including a proactive VANOS overhaul and a documented subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's primary known stress points. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the powertrain and drivetrain are in robust health, offering the raw, analog feedback sought by purists.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
